text: Got Fiona Apple to let me post video about song synch requests.  She didn’t think anyone would really care but I think it reminds us that we can all go beyond our personal self interests to find a way to help others, even from behind closed doors. #fionaapple #COVID19 #music https://t.co/gtPNvXLFfc
